  1. Hou7 goa2 bo5 hoat oan3-siaN
  Tui3 Hok-ek-hiaN put-heng7 cha2 koe3-sin, chiu7 hit-si5 i2-au7 i e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 Siok-cheng, chin chiaN3 si7 kan-kan khou2-khou2 khek-khin5 khek-khiam7, oa2-kho3 hit siang-chhiu2 ka7 lang5 choe3 saN lai5 khan nng7 e5 kiaN2. Toa7-han3--e5 ta-pou mia5 Bun5-hoa5, tng-si5 10 hoe3, se3-han3--e5 lu2 e5 kio3 Le7-hoa5 tng-si5 5 hoe3. I e5 tiong7-hu si7 pun2-su7 lang5, oah8 tong-si5 teh khui si5-pio2 tiam3, sin-lo5 chhiaN3 chin che7 e5. Na7 si7 chi2-moai7 chin leng5-lai7, i ka-ki7 siuN7 be7-hiau2 kng kio7, chiu7 m7-thang khui kio7-tiam3. Sui-bong2 u7 toa7-peh, sio2-chek, chong2-si7 bo5 lang5 pai3 Siong7-te3, jit8-thau5 chhiah iaN7-iaN7, sui5-lang5 kou3 siN3-mia7. Sou2-i2 i chek-si5 cheng2-li2, chiong sou2 khiam3--lang5 e5 heng5 chheng-chho2, se2 kau3 tit8 chhun bo5 loa7 che7, chiu7 poaN-jip8 chhi7-tiuN5-lai7. Ki-liong5 e5 seng-li2, ti7 chhi7-tiuN5 lai7 sim2-mih8 tou u7. I chiu7 ti7 tu2-ho2 e5 sou2-chai7 tui3 lang5 poaN5 chit8-keng se3-se3 e5 tiam3 ui7, bo2 kiaN2 chiu7 ti7 hia choe3 saN-khou3 tui3 chhai5-hong5 lai5 tou7-oah8. Siong7-te3 si-un lin5-bin2 i, i jiat8-sim khiN5-tiau5 ti7 Chu2, i ti7 kau3-hoe7 tng chip-su7, chiang2-li2 kau3-hoe7 e5 koe3-ke3, pang-chan7 Chu2-jit8-oh8, seng3-koa-pan, i si7 gim5 lu2 ke7-siaN e5 leng2-to7-chia2, i ia7 chiang2-li2 Lu2 Soat-to7-hoe7 e5 koe3-ke3, choe3 lang5 tiong-hou7, giam5-cheng3, chheng-pek8, hou7 kau3-hoe7 lai7-goa7 e5 lang5 sou2 chun-keng3. Tiong7-hu si2 hit ni5 i chiah 30 hoe3, chin che7 lang5 beh lai5 ka7 i choe3 chhin-chiaN5, i long2 ka7 lang5 the-si5, i kam-goan7 lo5-khou2 lai5 khan kiaN2. 
  Hit am3 chiah8-pa2 tak8-hang7 khoan2 chheng-chho2, chiu7 kio3 nng7 e5 kiaN2 lai5, chiau3-siong5 choe3 ka-teng5 le2-pai3. Bak8-chit8-nih8 Bun5-hoa5 i2-keng 11 hoe3, kok-bin5 hak8-hau7 3 lian5, Le7-hoa5 ia7 6 hoe3 lah. 
  Hian-khui seng3-si choe3-hoe2 gim5. 
