  3. Tan7 goan7 it-seng kap Chu2 saN-sui5, Toe3 Li2 eng2 bo5 li7-khui, Goan7 Chu2 eng7 kng chio3 goa2 chian5-tou5, Kap Li2 tang5 kau3 hit ui7. 
  (Chit siu2 si e5 chok-chia2 si7 jiat8-sim e5 lu2-tou5, i e5 bi7-hun-hu chin siau3-lian5 eng-chun3, tng beh kiat-hun e5 cheng5-jit8, ti7 ho5-nih8 se2-ek8, sit-chiok thut8-kha poah8 kau3 ti7 chhim e5 ui7, tui3 an2-ni sit-su7 eng2 piat8, chi2-moai7 ui7 chit-e5 su7 hoan5-lo2 ti3-piN7, it-seng sin-the2 loan2-jiok8, siong5-siong5 khah8-chhng5, chit siu2 chiu7-si7 i ti7 peN7-chhng5 tiong sou2 choe3 e5 si, che7-che7 lang5 ai3 gim5). 
  Hit am3 chiu7-si7 Siok-cheng e5 tiong7-hu si2 tui3 ni5 e5 jit8. Be7-bian2-tit siuN7 tioh8 cha2-cheng5 kap hian7-kim chiu7 bak8-sai2 si3-lam5-sui5. Na7-si7 i bo5 loe2-chi3, bak8-sai2 chhit-chhit leh, chiu7 hian-khui Seng3-keng lai5 thak8, Ko-lim5-to chian5-su 10 chiuN 10 chat, kong2 “Li2 ia7 boh8-tit ngauh8-ngauh8 liam7, chhin-chhiuN7 in tiong-kan u7 lang5 ngauh8-ngauh8 liam7, XXXX 13 chat: Lin2 sou2 tu2-tioh8 e5 chhi3 bo5 m7 si7 lang5 e5 siong5-su7; Siong7-te3 si7 sin3-sit8, bo5 beh hou7 lin2 tu2-tioh8 chhi3 ke3-thau5 ti7 lin2 sou2 oe7 tng; chiu7-si7 ti7 siu7 chhi3 e5 si5 beh soa3 khui thoat-chhut e5 lou7, hou7 lin2 tng oe7 khi3.” 
  Thak8 liau2 kio3 kiaN2 saN lun5 oat8-liam7 Si-phian 23 phiN, koh phoaN7 kiaN2 liam7 Sin3-keng, koh liam7 10 tiau5-kai3, Chu2 e5 ki5-to2-bun5, au7-lai5 i pun2-sin chiah eng7 kan2-tan e5 ki5-to2 lai5 soah. Jian5-au7 u7 kong2 tam7-poh8 pa-pa e5 su7 hou7 tai7-ke siau3-liam7 chai7-seN e5 pa-pa si7 ho5-teng2 e5 thiaN3-sioh in. Choe3 chit-khoan2 e5 ki3-liam7, soa3 kou2-le7 kiaN2-ji5 tioh8 lip8-chi3, kian-sim sin3 Chu2, oa2-kho3 Chu2 jin7-chin lai5 chin3-pou7. Sio2-moai7 Le7-hoa5 se3-han3 khah be7-hiau2 thiaN, na7-si7 Bun5-hoa5 ku3-ku3 tim3-thau5, bak8-sai2 koa3 tiam3 bak8-kiN5, chhiu2 tiN7 kun5 thau5-bu2, chhui3-tun5 ka7 an5-an5, ku3-ku3 leng2-siu7 lau7-bo2 e5 ka3-si7, sim-te2 lip8-se7 kian-sim beh siu2 ma-ma e5 hoan-hu3, lip8-chi3 choe3 koai-kiaN2 lai5 eng5-kng Siong7-te3 po3-tap pa-pa, ma-ma e5 in. Keh-jit8 piaN3-sau3 teh phak8-mih8 e5 si5, chiong lai7-bin7 e5 mih8 long2 theh8 chhut-lai5 goa7-bin7 phak8-jit8, hut-jian5 ti7 keh-a2-teng2, bo5 teh kah e5 mi5-phoe7 lai7, mi5-phoe7 chih ho2-ho2 siu ti7 hia, ti7 hit lai7-bin7 khoaN3-tioh8 chit8 e5 choa2-khe-a2, lai7-bin7 u7 te2 chiN5, u7 chit8-kak--e5, ia7 u7 nng7-kak--e5, ia7 u7 gou7-kak--e5, ia7 u7 gin5-phio3, long2-chong2 u7 4 khou goa7-gin5. I e5 lau7-bo2 chin ki5-koai3, mng7 bo5 khi3 thak8-chheh e5 Le7-hoa5, che si7 sim2-mih8 chiN5, Le7-hoa5 io5-thau5 m7 kong2, khah mng7 tou m7 kong2, ma-ma mng7 i chaiN2-iuN7 li2 mng7 m7 kong2? I kong2, “Ko-ko kong2 m7-thang kong2,” an2-ni Le7-hoa5 chin siu2 iok, i thiaN3 a-ko. Lau7-bo2 chiu7 bo5 koh pek--i, kong2, “Ho2, theng3-hau7 lin2 ko-ko to3--lai5, goa2 chiah lai5 mng7 i, an2-choaN2 e7 chhang3 hiah che7 chiN5 tiam3 phoe7-lai7, bo5 hou7 ma-ma chai, koh mng7 m7 kong2.” 
  (khiam3 te7 27 ki5, 1960 ni5 5 geh8) 
