  3. SaN-khoan2 chhu2-li2-hoat. 
  Tui3 kong3-phoa3 hoe-kan tak8-lang5 poe5 5 khou-gin5, Siok-cheng e5 chhu2-li2-hoat lan2 i2-keng chai. Thian-lai5-a7 to3-khi3 beh ka7 in lau7-bu2 theh8, in lau7-bu2 kong2 i m7-chai. Chiong chit-e5 su7 ka7 in lau7-pe7 kong2. Toa7-tiau5-ah, peh-khi2-lai5 thiau3, chek-si5 khi3 sa chit8-ki tin5-tiau5 chhin-chhiuN7 teh but8-gu5 an2-ni tit8-tut8, chhoh koh kiau7. Thian-lai5-a7 bun3 tui3 toh-kha loh8-khi3, koh thoa chhut-lai5 eng7 kha cham3, tng3 lap-che7 loh8-khi3, chhia-to2 oaN2-tau2-a2 kong3-phoa3 chin che7 te3 oaN2, in lau7-pe7 koh-khah khi3, me7 i khoaN3 beh khi3 to2-ui7 si2, kin2 khi3 si2. Thian-lai5-a7 chu7 an2-ni khau3 tui3 goa7-bin7 chhut-khi3, kau3 in lau7-pe7 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 e5 ui7 bak8-sai2 chhit-chhit leh, khui-chhui3 chhoh in lau7-pe7, pang3-tiau in lau7-pe7 to m7-thang chiah8 lau7, i tek-khak beh po3-oan. Long2 bo5 kong2 beh heng5--lang5, hit-am3 Thian-lai5-a7 khi3 goa7-khau2 liu5, bo5 chiah8, liu5 kau3 chin am3 chiah so5 to3--lai5. In lau7-pe7 tu2 gu7 u7 oa2-chun5, kou3 chhut-hoe3 ia7 bo5 koh mng7. 
  Keh bin5-a2-chai3 Thian-lai5-a7 khi3 haN2 Hian2-chou2 ka3 i the3 i chhut-chiN5 thang poe5, na7 bo5 beh cheng--i. Hian2-chou2 saN-a2-te7 lai7-bin7 put-si5 tou u7 chiN5, na7 pin5-toaN7 kiaN5 sui5-pian7 chio peng5-iu2 che7 saN-lian2-chhia to3-khi3 ka7 lang5 chhut-chiN5, gou7-khou-gin5 i si7 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3, koh Lim5 gi7-oan5 kap Tan5 Toa7-tiau5 ti7 bou2 hong-bin7 si7 u7 am3-thong e5 sou2-chai7, chiu7-si7 ti7 chau2-su e5 si5, Lim5 sian-siN chin su-iau3 Toa7-tiau5 e5 pang-chan7. Sou2-i2 Hian2-chou2 e5 chiN5, mih8 si7 hou7 Thian-lai5-a7 eng7 bu5-sou3, nng2--e5 ia7 beh i, nge7--e5 ia7 beh i, Hian2-chou2 na7 hou7 lang5 khi-hu7, Thian-lai5-a7 ia7 the3 i choe3 kun5-thau5 tiam. Sou2-i2 Hian2-chou2 eng7 chiN5 phaN3, Thian-lai5-a7 e5 kun5-thau5-bu2 toa7-liap8, Bun5-hoa5 ti7 in tiong-kan, chhin-chhiuN7 chiN2-a2 chhap ti7 khong2-chhiok, kap chhai5-long5 tiong. M7-ku2 si7 tong5-kip-seng, ji5-chhiaN2 beh khi3, beh to3-lai5 long2 siang7 tiau5-lou7, sou2-i2 m7 kap in kiaN5 ia7 hou7 in chau-that, beh kap in kiaN5 ia7 hou7 in chhi2-ti7, sit8-chai7 si7 chin oh choe3 lang5. 
  Koh kong2 to3-tng2--lai5 piaN3-sau3 hit-jit8, tak8-hang7 mih8 theh8 chhut lai5 phak8, peng2-peng2 hiah-e5 bo5 lou7-eng7 e5 mih8, Siok-cheng khoaN3-choe3 bo5 lou7-eng7--e5 long2 ka7 i hiat-kak8. Ki5-tiong u7 hiah-e5 chhit-chap8-tang5 peh-chap8-thih, put-tong7 li2-khian e5 mih8, Le7-hoa5 liah8 choe3 chin po2-poe3, pau chit8-pau chit8-pau un5-un5-a2 siu ho2-se3, lian5 chit8-sian liu3-phi2 liu3-phi2 bin7 ku7-khi3 niau-niau e5 ang5-a2, oa2 chiaN5-chhioh toa7, sou2 chheng7 e5 saN ia7 ku7-ku7-khi3 lah, ia7 chin m7-kam siu ho2-se3, Siok-cheng long2 khoaN3 choe3 bo5 lou7-eng7 ka7 i hiat-kak8, u7 e5 ka7 i pang3 hoe2-sio. 
  Le7-hoa5 khi3 thak8 Iu3-ti7-hng5 to3--lai5, khoaN3 chit8-e7 toa7 m7-kam, chin7 sou3 e7 khi3 khioh to3-tng2--lai5, tek8-piat8 hit sian ang5-a2 e5 saN u7 hou7 hoe2 sio-tioh8, chhiu2-kut chit8-ki ia7 sio2-khoa2 sio-tioh8, Le7-hoa5 kin2-khi3 tui3 hoe2-tiong kiu3 i chhut, lau5 bak8-sai2 chin m7-kam. Le7-hoa5 sui-jian5 si7 6 hoe3, ki5-sit8 chiah u7 5 hoe3 chiok, ni5-boe2 ut-hoe3 e5 kiaN2, chin m7-kam, khioh lai5 pho7 tiam3 heng-cheng5, kin2 khioh ma-ma e5 pou3-liau5-a2 lai5 ka7 i pau-chhiu2, na2-chun2 hou7-su7 chit8-iuN7 e5 koan-sim hoan7-chia2, koh kiu5 ma-ma ka7 i choe3 sin-saN. Siok-cheng khi2-thau5 khoaN3 liau2 ia7 ho2-khi3, ia7 ho2-chhio3, chong2-si7 au7-lai5 chiu7 siuN7 eng-kai tioh8 the2-thiap se3-kiaN2 e5 sim, chun-tiong7 se3-kiaN2 e5 sou2-iu2-koan5, mih8 si7 i e5, bo5 kap i chham-siong5, bo5 tit se3-kiaN2 e5 liong7-kai2, sui5-pian7 chiong lang5 khoaN3 choe3 ke-hoe2 e5 mih8 ka7 lang5 hiat-kak8, si7 bu5-si7 lang5 e5 jin5-koan5 e5 chun-giam5, koh tek8-piat tui3 i e5 ho2 peng5-iu2 “Bi2-le7” (hit-sian ang5-a2 e5 mia5), ka7 i liah8 khi3 hou7 hoe2-sio koh-khah m7-tioh8, koe3-khi3 Bi2-le7 kap i khun3, hou7 i pho7, hou7 i aiN7, choe3 i e5 lang5-kheh hou7 i chhiaN2, i bo5 ti7-teh, lan2 chiu7 chiong i sou2 khoaN3 choe3 ho2 peng5-iu2 e5, ka7 i hiat hou7 hoe2-sio, chin-chiaN3 siong-tioh8 se3-kiaN2 e5 iu2-ji5-kam2, bok8-koai3 Le7-hoa5 siong-sim. TaN tioh8 oan5-seng5 i e5 nng2-sim e5 heng5-ui5 chiah ho2, siat-su2 lan2 na7 nge7-nge7 ka7 i chhiuN2 hiat-kak8, kong2 m7-thiaN, soa3 ka7 i phah, kong2 i sam-pat, kau3 hiah toa7-han3 lah iau2 teh sng2 ang5-a2, an2-ni chit8-sut-a2 tou bo5 li7-ek hit-e5 gin2-na2 e5 cheng-sin5 kau3-iok8, koh tian-to3 hou7 i giau5-gi5 lau7-bu2 e5 au2-hoaiN5, bo5 cheng5, bo5 thiaN3-sim, i beh m7-goan7 li2, khoaN3-khin lau7-bo2 e5 sou2-choe3, beh it-seng ki3-tit li2 e5 ia2-ban5, m7-na7 bo5 poe5-iok8 i e5 chu5-sim, iu2-gi5, koh hou7 i phau7 bo5-han7 e5 siong-pi-kam2, kap m7-kam-goan7 lau7-bu2 bo5 cheng5-li2, ko-ap-tek chhiu2-toaN7 e5 khoan2-thai7. 
  Siok-cheng siuN7-lai5 siuN7-khi3 chiu7 kin2 koh chiong lan5-san-pou3 the3 “Bi2-le7” choe3 sin-saN, ia7 tui3 Le7-hoa5 hoe7 sit-le2, ka7 i kong2, Ma-ma chit8-si5 siuN7 bo5 tioh8, be7 ki3-tit mng7 Le7-hoa5 iau2 u7 khiam3-eng7 Bi2-le7 a2-bo5.” Tek-khak m7-thang bu5-si7 se3-kiaN2 e5 chu7-chun-sim. 
  Le7-hoa5 chiu7 chhit i e5 bak8-sai2, bin7 tng2-chhio3, pho7 i e5 Bi2-le7 lai5 pheng7 tiam3 ma-ma e5 heng-cheng5. Ti7 hia piau2-hian7 jin5-kan e5 un-loan2, chiah soah-khi3 hiam2-hiam2 sio-si2 se3-kiaN2 e5 ho2-peng5-iu2, leng2-khok hiong-sat, cham5-jim2 e5 su7-kiaN7, hit-e5 hong-pho chiah piN5-tiaN7. Lan2 iau3-kin2 tioh8 the2-thiap se3-kiaN2 iu3-chiN2 e5 sim-leng5. 
  (khiam3 te7 29 ki5, 1960 ni5 7 geh8) 
  5. “Phah hou7 li2 si2” 
  U7 chit8 jit8 Le7-hoa5 tui3 iu3-ti7-hng5 to3--lai5, seng-khu hui-siong5 la5-sam5, goan5-in si7 ti7 iu3-ti7-hng5 kap lang5 sng2-chui2, iu3-ti7-hng5 u7 phun3-chui2-ti5, ti5 te2 u7 chhi7 kim-hi5, hit jit8 kap ki5-u5 e5 gin2-na2 ti7 po2-bo2 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 e5 si5 thau khi3 sng2-chui2, sio hou3, chin sim-sek, chiok hoaN-hi2, sou2-i2 seng-khu soa3 phah-tam5. Au7-lai5 koh khi3 soa-a2-tui sng2, sou2-i2 seng-khu ko7 kau3 ou kui2-kui2, to3--lai5 e5 si5 ma-ma khoaN3 chit8-e7 hui-siong5 siu7-khi3, ti7 choe3-saN e5 pou3-chhng5 teng2 u7 chhioh, sui5-pian7 giah8 khi2--lai5 lian5-lian5 bo5 keng2 sou2-chai7 ka7 i but8 chin-che7-e7, chin khi3, sim phok8-phok8-chheng2, chhiu2 phi7-phi7-chhoah kong2, “But8 chit8-e7 thau2-khui3 leh, e7 hou7 li2 khi3--si2, ian7-thau5 ka7 li2 kong2 seng-khu tioh8 m7-thang bak kiaN-lang5, li2 chiah thiau-i3-kou3 bak kiaN-lang5, an2-ni kiam2 e7 khoaN3-tit, chit8 seng-khu be7 su na2 kui2, ia7 teh lau5-phiN7, khoaN3 tioh8 chin-chheh”, m7-goan7 koh ka7 i liam3 chit8-e7 kong2, “Be7 tit lin2 pe7 si2, lioh8-a2 chiu7 leng2-tioh8 lau5-phiN7, li2 ia7 kaN2 sng2-chui2.” Le7-hoa5 tit8-tit8 hau2, ia7 thiaN3, ia7 kiaN. Tu2 hit si5 Le7-hoa5 e5 lau7-su, po2-bo2 tui3 hia koe3, i ia7 si7 lan2 kau3-hoe7 e5 chi2-moai7, i u7 thak8 koe3 lan2 Sin5-hak8-iN7 e5 po2-bo2-kho, iu3-ti7-hng5 ia7 si7 lan2 kau3-hoe7 siat--e5. I tui3 hia koe3 thiaN Le7-hoa5 teh hau2, chiu7 oat lai5 ka7 i khoaN3, khoaN3 Siok-cheng chip-su7 khi3 phut-phut, chhiu2 iau2-ku2 giah8 chhioh, chiu7 oa2-khi3 eng7 chhio3-iong5 lai5 khou2-khng3 Siok-cheng chip-su7, soa3 hoe7 sit-le2 kong2, “Chin sit-le2, in-ui7 goa2 sit chu3-i3 e5 kam-tok, sou2-i2 hou7 i khi3 bak-chui2, bak kau3 hiah tam5.” Siok-cheng chip-su7 ki3-jian5 khoaN3 po2-bo2 hiah chhio3-iong5, hiah chhin-chhiat teh hoe7, ka-ki7 ia7 chin phaiN2-se3, chhioh pang3 leh, chiu7 khan Le7-hoa5 lai5 oaN7-saN. 
  Hit am3 tng gin2-na2 khi3 hioh-khun3 e5 si5 po2-bo2 lai5 chhoe7 Siok-cheng che7, kap i tam5-lun7 gin2-na2 kau3-iok8 e5 su7, kong2 khi2 hian7-chai7 e5 kau3-iok8 su-tiau5 (kau3-iok8 siong7 su-siuN2 e5 tiau5-liu5) kap eng2-koe3 chin toa7 e5 koh-iuN7 choe3 toa7 koh-iuN7 e5 kui2-na7 tiam2. 
